Can't Perform Installation Step

You must first choose partition and file-system types.
If you have already done that, maybe there is some problem
with your selection. Check especially the root partition
(mountpoint /). The current 'mounts' info is shown below:

Mountpoint  Partition  Format [Format tweaks]

:::!dscript
cat ${TEMPDIR}/mounts | sed 's|!|     |g'
